    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The widget doesn't support multiple instance the way you're doing it because they are not aware of the others and the default behaviour. Maybe you can work around that by implementing a [custom widget](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/guides/customization.html) using the [connectSortBySelector](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectSortBySelector.html) [connector](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors.html)?",
